{"tid":2047421,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁子超強烈建議祿泉樓居民接受14日醫學監察停工停課","createTime":"2020-06-02T05:51:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T02:47:47.000Z","uid":166360,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3edbdf3accd0610fc6e9402d3b98507f893675f4","tid":2047421,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:51:53.000Z","msg":"梁子超強烈建議祿泉樓居民接受14日醫學監察停工停課<br />\n2020-06-02 HKT 12:21<br />\n<br />\n醫學會傳染病顧問委員會主席梁子超表示，沙田瀝源邨祿泉樓的居民毋須撤離，但由於檢測不能避免有假陰性，為穩妥起見，強烈建議他們接受14日醫學監察，停止高危活動，包括上班及上學，又說居民不應搬到親戚的家居住。至於附近社區人士如果有呼吸道病徵，應該接受篩檢。<br />\n<br />\n梁子超在本台節目《千禧年代》說，今次會否造成大型傳播，要視乎未來數日的追蹤情況，包括確診夫婦近期去過的地方及接觸過的人士。他相信只要祿泉樓所有住戶都完成檢測，剔出傳播源，做好消毒工作，祿泉樓是安全，不過一次的篩檢不足以排除未來14日仍有繼發性個案，因此居民應該接受醫學監測。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529721-20200602.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529721-20200602.htm&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbcjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=9ac5a5aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529721-20200602.htm&h=87c21689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529721-20200602.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2d36d0db648d00d9fe9cf53a70c80e2074de81a0","tid":2047421,"uid":176282,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:54:05.000Z","msg":"建議？wfc"},{"pid":"9978a01685057df0e561518da3abf8dae2c56fc8","tid":2047421,"uid":166360,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3edbdf3accd0610fc6e9402d3b98507f893675f4","tid":2047421,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:51:53.000Z","msg":"梁子超強烈建議祿泉樓居民接受14日醫學監察停工停課<br />\n2020-06-02 HKT 12:21<br />\n<br />\n醫學會傳染病顧問委員會主席梁子超表示，沙田瀝源邨祿泉樓的居民毋須撤離，但由於檢測不能避免有假陰性，為穩妥起見，強烈建議他們接受14日醫學監察，停止高危活動，包括上班及上學，又說居民不應搬到親戚的家居住。至於附近社區人士如果有呼吸道病徵，應該接受篩檢。<br />\n<br />\n梁子超在本台節目《千禧年代》說，今次會否造成大型傳播，要視乎未來數日的追蹤情況，包括確診夫婦近期去過的地方及接觸過的人士。他相信只要祿泉樓所有住戶都完成檢測，剔出傳播源，做好消毒工作，祿泉樓是安全，不過一次的篩檢不足以排除未來14日仍有繼發性個案，因此居民應該接受醫學監測。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529721-20200602.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529721-20200602.htm&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbcjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=9ac5a5aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529721-20200602.htm&h=87c21689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529721-20200602.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:57:41.000Z","msg":"祿泉樓居民有上班及上學的權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7420b90aa0bbc0341e6b7dda0bc0a85f1ca5c572","tid":2047421,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:05:05.000Z","msg":"宜家祿泉樓同武漢一樣咁危險<br />\n有fd做wiki都開始唔送果度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9549cd038ee9821831cb4f74957df8be601fd94f","tid":2047421,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:06:17.000Z","msg":"走哂去播毒了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5e378e111b457a75c2e34c78c87b8e7ceba5ec","tid":2047421,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7420b90aa0bbc0341e6b7dda0bc0a85f1ca5c572","tid":2047421,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:05:05.000Z","msg":"宜家祿泉樓同武漢一樣咁危險<br />\n有fd做wiki都開始唔送果度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:07:26.000Z","msg":"梗係唔撚送，保險唔包"},{"pid":"27fea0b56344251f8622cf613d6838da5acd686d","tid":2047421,"uid":205346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:07:30.000Z","msg":"唔好阻我搵食"},{"pid":"d3b45c47ce51417b14bc6d611647e2633ba37575","tid":2047421,"uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27fea0b56344251f8622cf613d6838da5acd686d","t